{"tid":2309257,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"中天電視台前企圖自焚 男子在門口大喊：「為什麼要開除王又正！」","createTime":"2020-12-02T12:02:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-03T04:01:07.000Z","uid":310867,"like":11,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"47198642a02fb8c6f54e929b16206779d6448715","tid":2309257,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T12:02:24.000Z","msg":"位在台北市內湖區的中天電視台，今天（2日）晚間有一名男子（約40歲）在門口大喊：「為什麼要開除王又正！」後竟潑汽油自焚，造成自己上半身、臉部2度燒傷，意識清醒，電視台人員撲滅火勢阻止，已由救護車送往醫院急救，警方趕往現場了解。有民眾拍下男子全身著火的驚悚畫面<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GSw1FUg.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGSw1FUg.png&h=706e9c93&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20201202/CK3TXZ3GJFEF3A6PP3PJW35EI4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201202%2FCK3TXZ3GJFEF3A6PP3PJW35EI4%2F&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOVTAjexNHzxSh3iQmMoU3XE%3D&h=e56c1578\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201202%2FCK3TXZ3GJFEF3A6PP3PJW35EI4%2F&h=5d2ecc2a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/local/20201202/CK3TXZ3GJFEF3A6PP3PJW35EI4/</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據了解，中天新聞換照遭NCC駁回，引發群眾熱議後，該名男子到中天門口自焚，大喊「為什麼要開除王又正！」遭到警方阻止，詳細事發原因仍待進一步調查釐清。 <br />\n<a href=\"https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-12-02/503046\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnewtalk.tw%2Fnews%2Fview%2F2020-12-02%2F503046&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOVTAjexNHzxSh3iQmMoU3XE%3D&h=c3e84ac5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://newtalk.tw/news/view/2020-12-02/503046</a>"},{"pid":"5153ce0ece431f26e8ddc2838ca28459d8f04d81","tid":2309257,"uid":266010,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T12:03:11.000Z","msg":"勇氣可嘉"},{"pid":"355ec5deef4a0dd81ac7c3f2bc0395f0323f0c02","tid":2309257,"uid":121546,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T12:03:26.000Z","msg":"有線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"357754536ea7cdb86d8474aad083fce4e33b3a21","tid":2309257,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"355ec5deef4a0dd81ac7c3f2bc0395f0323f0c02","tid":2309257,"uid":121546,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T12:03:26.000Z","msg":"有線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T12:03:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2edb76e3dbfd0845a5ed05e8ecf456ae889cc9f7","tid":2309257,"uid":310867,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T12:05:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/life/20201202/KT6WHD5GGRETTDQECLWC6TJTCQ/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flife%2F20201202%2FKT6WHD5GGRETTDQECLWC6TJTCQ%2F&d=u42ujRIT%2FE%2FeodHrCKN%2BOVTAjexNHzxSh3iQmMoU3XE%3D&h=4dc29af0\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Flife%2F20201202%2FKT6WHD5GGRETTDQECLWC6TJTCQ%2F&h=bef472a8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/life/20201202/KT6WHD5GGRETTDQECLWC6TJTCQ/</a><br />\n<br />\n中天新聞台換照未予通過，表定下周五（11日）晚間12時將是最後播送期限，針對空下來的52頻道，除中嘉、大豐各申請以寰宇新聞台、CNN替代，北都、全國數位、東部的東亞、洄瀾等系統業者則申請暫空頻，另超過半數系統業者都還沒送頻道規劃，國家通訊傳播委員會（NCC）表示，民眾如認為缺少頻道權益受損，可要求無條件解約。<br />\n<br />\n不過中天停播、頻道變更作業仍在進行中，由於停播期限在即，在這之前，也僅剩一次NCC委員會議，<span class=\"red\">幾乎肯定無法在停播之前就決定好替代頻道，NCC表示，屆時技術上可先跳頻處理，也就是民眾選台時，會直接從51台跳至53台，但系統業者仍須在中天新聞台停播之前，送頻道變更申請到該會。</span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"302067791c264084c04856f061706bb959b324e2","tid":2309257,"uid":310867,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"355ec5deef4a0dd81ac7c3f2bc0395f0323f0c02","tid":2309257,"uid":121546,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T12:03:26.000Z","msg":"有線<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T12:09:43.000Z","msg":"唔係為cut台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"151435b780c34518c7d810ad3fb6c7a934a2cf30","tid":2309257,"uid":269202,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T12:13:25.000Z","msg":"中國人竟然<br />\n<br />\n係駐台大使館扇動以外<br />\n<br />\n自決舉行暴力示威<br />\n<br />\n實在是觸犯了國安法的民族恥辱<br />\n<br />\n應永久取消其及家屬中國國民身份或護照"},{"pid":"cdf35465af0837b70b4ce85fdd4aa15f7172045e","tid":2309257,"uid":290118,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T12:14:08.000Z","msg":"同志<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d45d031e0be3b2ae4512bc2314553f49a3a1198d","tid":2309257,"uid":310867,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-02T12:14:15.000Z","msg":"警方經查後表示，該名孫姓男子（60歲）今晚7時許步入中天電視台大門，拿一個紅包請警衛轉交給中天主播戴立綱後便轉身離開，不料走出大門後，竟突然朝自己身上點火，瞬間上半身起火，變成一團火球，警衛見狀趕緊呼喊求救，並拿滅火器衝上前協助滅火。<br />\n<br />\n警方指出，孫男疑似持揮發性液體朝自己身上潑灑並點火後，造成全身起火，孫男周邊還有許多脫下的衣物也在旁邊燃起火勢，<span class=\"red\">孫男自焚時，意識清楚，在中天前廣場走來走去，並大喊，「挺中天」、「為什麼開除王又正？王又正到哪去了？」、「說關就關」，</span>疑似是中天粉絲，警方已封鎖現場，蒐證了解孫男自焚動機。<br />\n<br />\n針對中天電視台前今晚自焚情病人情況，個案目前意識清醒，醫師正在搶救中。<br />\n<br />\n似孔乙己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9f31281b17f7b22109d866371d4f2379ea1a5f8a","tid":2309257,"uid":54516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score